# Taxomet Taxi Management System — Comprehensive Analysis
*Based on live demo at `https://demo.taxomet.ru/` — verified step-by-step from real screenshots*

---

## 1. System Architecture & Modules

The system is a server-rendered SPA dispatcher dashboard. It consists of two navigation layers:

### Top Navigation Bar (always visible)
| Label | Description |
|---|---|
| **Монитор** | Real-time order dispatch console — the main work area |
| **Операторы (1)** | Operator/admin user management. Number = active count |
| **Водители (0)** | Driver registry with live status. Number = online count |
| **Автомобили** | Full vehicle fleet catalog |
| **Допуски (0)** | Document verification queue for drivers/vehicles |
| **Журнал заказов** | Full historical order database with advanced filtering |
| **Звонки** | Telephony log with call recordings/SIP integration |

### Sidebar (≡ hamburger icon, top-left) — Two Sections

**Справочники (Directories/Configuration):**
| Item | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Классы автомобилей | Vehicle class groups (Economy, Business, Minivan, etc.) |
| Опции автомобилей | Extra options (child seat, pet, cargo) |
| Тарифы для водителей | Commission/fixed tariff rules per driver |
| Безлимиты для водителей | Unlimited shift packages for drivers |
| Услуги для водителей | Additional driver services |
| Службы такси и тарифы | Core taxi service config with client-facing tariffs |
| Геозоны / Границы | Polygon geographic zone editor |
| Трансферы (сетки тариф.) | Fixed-price transfer grids |
| Цены в геозонах | Price overrides per geozone |
| Очереди (стоянки) | Driver queue/parking spot management |

**Настройки (Settings):**
| Item | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Общие настройки | Global system settings (timezone, IPs, distribution logic) |
| Настройки телефонии | SIP/PBX configuration |
| Настройки допусков | Document review settings |
| Загрузка карт (старые) | Legacy map tile importer |
| Редактор карт | Interactive custom map editor |
| Платежные системы | Payment gateway integrations |
| Он-лайн кассы (54-ФЗ) | Russian online fiscal cash register compliance |
| Настройки обменника | Order exchange/partner network settings |
| Настройки рейтингов | Driver/client rating algorithm settings |
| Регистрация водителей | Driver self-registration portal settings |
| Шаблоны договоров | Contract templates for drivers |
| Обновление ПО | Software/firmware update manager |

**Финансы (Financial — also in sidebar):**
| Item | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Клиенты | Client CRM: phone, order history, bonuses |
| Черные списки | Blacklist management (phone-based bans) |
| Цены на топливо | Fuel cost tracking for expense reporting |
| Журнал смен | Driver shift journal |
| Касса | Operator cash flow: balances, payouts, deposits |
| Отчет по эквайрингу | Online payment acquiring report |
| Безналичные расчеты | Corporate/cashless settlement reports |
| Контроль | Operational control dashboard |

