## 2. Monitor Module — Deep Dive

The Monitor is the primary real-time workspace.

![Monitor Map Tab](file:///C:/Users/user/.gemini/antigravity/brain/b15b8215-d5af-4543-a47f-a9a943008a8c/artifacts/monitor_map.png)

### Monitor Sub-tabs (verified from live UI):
| Tab | Label | Description |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | **Текущие заказы (0)** | Live table of active orders. Count shown. |
| 2 | **Предварительные (0)** | Scheduled/future orders. Count shown. |
| 3 | **Обменник (0)** | Order exchange marketplace with partner services. |
| 4 | **Карта** | Full-screen OpenStreetMap with live driver pins. |
| 5 | **Чат (0)** | Dispatcher-to-driver messaging. Count = unread. |
| 6 | **Системное (0)** | System/event log feed. |
| 7 | **Тревоги (0)** | Emergency alerts / panic button events from drivers. |

### Map Controls (Карта sub-tab):
- **+/−** zoom buttons (top-left of map)
- **☑ Группировать водителей** — checkbox to cluster driver markers
- **Имена** — button to toggle name labels on driver markers
- **OpenStreetMap** tiles (© OpenStreetMap contributors)
- Status bar: "Входящая линия: ошибка (Offline)" — SIP line status
- **Очередь:** field showing dispatcher queue status

### Status Bar (always visible, top of page):
- **Общ. касса: 0 руб.** — Total cash balance
- **ПО: 100 руб.** — Advance payment
- **ONLINE** (green) — System connection status

### New Order Button:
- `+ Новый заказ (Alt+F1)` — primary action button (yellow/orange)

