## 8. UX/UI Evaluation

| Aspect | Details |
|---|---|
| **Layout** | Three-zone: Top nav bar / Sub-tab row / Content area |
| **Real-time display** | Live counters in all Monitor tabs (e.g., `Текущие заказы (0)`) |
| **Color coding** | 🟢 Free · 🟡 On order · 🔴 Offline driver status icons |
| **Keyboard-first** | Alt+F1 (new order), Ctrl+Enter (submit), Esc (close) |
| **Map** | OpenStreetMap, full-tab view, driver clustering toggle, name labels |
| **In-form map** | New Order form embeds a live mini-map for address validation |
| **Status bar** | Persistent header shows: logged-in user, cash balance, SIP status, ONLINE indicator |
| **Density** | High-density ERP style — no whitespace wasted, max information per screen |
| **Responsiveness** | Designed for 1:1 desktop; not mobile-optimized |

