## 9. Primary Data Entities

| Entity | Key Fields |
|---|---|
| **Order** (Заказ) | `id`, `phone`, `service_id`, `driver_id`, `operator_id`, `pickup_address`, `dropoff_address`, `stops[]`, `distance`, `class_id`, `tariff_id`, `cashless_account_id`, `use_bonuses`, `price`, `status`, `created_at`, `scheduled_at`, `completed_at`, `comment`, `printed_receipt` |
| **Driver** (Водитель) | `id`, `group_id`, `callsign`, `last_name`, `first_name`, `middle_name`, `phone`, `login`, `password_hash`, `tariff_group_id`, `unlimited_tariff_group_id`, `max_credit`, `comment`, `status` (free/busy/offline), `current_coords`, `device_id` |
| **Vehicle** (Автомобиль) | `id`, `plate`, `make`, `model`, `color`, `ownership_type` (driver/company), `driver_id`, `taxi_service_ids[]`, `class_ids[]`, `option_ids[]` |
| **VehicleClass** | `id`, `group_id`, `name` (Эконом/Комфорт/Бизнес/VIP/Минивэн...) |
| **VehicleOption** | `id`, `name` (детское кресло, перевозка животных, etc.), `price_modifier` |
| **TaxiService** | `id`, `name`, `driver_group_ids[]`, `settlement`, `priority`, `auto_selection_type`, `client_tariff_config` |
| **DriverTariff** | `id`, `name`, `type` (commission/fixed), `value`, `schedule`, `priority`, `active` |
| **Tariff** (client-facing) | `id`, `service_id`, `class_id`, `base_price`, `price_per_km`, `price_per_min`, `min_price`, `free_wait_min`, `extra_wait_price` |
| **Geozone** | `id`, `name`, `polygon_coords[]`, `type` (city boundary / service zone) |
| **GeozonePricing** | `geozone_from_id`, `geozone_to_id`, `tariff_id`, `price_override` |
| **Queue** | `id`, `name`, `location_point`, `radius`, `driver_ids[]` |
| **Operator** | `id`, `login`, `name`, `role`, `cash_balance`, `advance_balance`, `active` |
| **Client** | `id`, `phone`, `name`, `bonus_balance`, `order_history[]`, `blacklisted` |
| **CallLog** | `id`, `timestamp`, `phone_from`, `phone_to`, `type` (inbound/outbound), `operator_id`, `service_id`, `duration_total`, `duration_wait`, `duration_talk`, `status` |
| **CashTransaction** | `id`, `operator_id`, `type` (payout/deposit), `amount`, `timestamp`, `linked_order_id` |

